opening_comment: https://www.openstreetmap.org/relation/6572464 Is it possible that Just√∏y is a correct or at least alternative name?
closing_comment: The proper name is Just√∏ya, which is basically 'The Just√∏y' and the name generally used when referring to the island. The word Just√∏y will be found in names like 'Just√∏ybroa' - 'The Just√∏y Bridge' og 'Just√∏yveien' - 'The Just√∏y Road' because the definite article -a or -en (equivalent to 'the') moves to the last word in the compound word. That said, some places it is referred to as simply Just√∏y, among other places in the wikipedia article about it, so I think this warrants adding it as an alternative name.
